Here is an especially beautiful drive-by of @villalaCassinella , from our friends @takemyhearteverywhere 
Be sure to look at it in reels so that you get the full effect. 
As we know, this iconic villa is located between the also iconic @villa_balbiano  and @villadelbalbianello , and it is accessible only by boat- so romantic ❤️

 Remember- this villa is NOT owned by Richard Branson, no matter what anyone tells you. 
Have a great Saturday, everyone!

node.text:
Happy Wednesday with this perfect video of the Plane Tree Walk at Villa Melzi d’Eril @giardinidivillamelzi , one of the more famous parts of the garden, from the gorgeous gallery of our great friend @pinkines
Be sure to watch it in reels so that you can see it in full screen – it’s very beautiful💚
Wishing everyone a great day!

PS- We looked at this villa and garden in 2016, use #villamelzijy to see more, especially some very rare interior images.
